                            Pacific Investment Management Company LLC (PIMCO) (sub-advisor)                        


Portfolio manager David Hammer, leads his New York-based team from PIMCO to sub-advise a long/short credit strategy for Salient. The team’s ability to short bonds and employ a variety of hedging techniques provides the strategy the opportunity to offer income and adaptability to portfolios.



